cdata.name: Quanta
cdata.desc:
Quanta PLC is a decentralised lottery ecosystem developed via blockchain technology allowing users to have a participation in the lottery platform. Quanta's platform enables the users to have a cryptocurrency wallet to receive affiliate rewards, play on RANDAO (Winner selection) & Lottery. Additionally, the platform will have also feature a cryptocurrency exchange.

The Quanta PLC issued an Ethereum-based ERC 20 token named as QNTU. The QNTU is used as a payment method and as a reward in the affiliate program within the Quanta ecosystem.
